text: KSEC (95.7 FM) is a radio station broadcasting a Mexican Regional format. Licensed to Bentonville, Arkansas, United States, it serves the Fayetteville (Northwest Arkansas) area. The station is currently owned by La Zeta 95.7 Inc. ==External links== * Category:Regional Mexican radio stations in the United States SEC SEC Category:Radio stations established in 1982 Category:1982 establishments in Arkansas
